        <item>
            <title>小紅書充斥假證有網紅更到廉署打卡，或涉及偽造證件及冒充廉政公署人員</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 10:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ICAC]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1261157</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">近日一名自稱為「時尚博主」和模特兒的劉姓女子，分享她來港旅遊時的打卡照並上傳到小紅書，而其中一張在廉政公署門外的打卡照卻引起爭議。這名女網紅在照片中一身黑色西裝的打扮，打卡時出示「首席調查主任」委任證，被指偽造證件及冒充廉政公署人員。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261178 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560141-454x580.jpg" alt="" width="454" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560141-454x580.jpg 454w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560141.jpg 705w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 454px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560306-498x580.jpg" alt="" width="498" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560306-498x580.jpg 498w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024090560306.jpg 773w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 498px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：抖音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261164 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458304253_1589645195-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458304253_1589645195-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458304253_1589645195.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2021470/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BAICAC-%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E7%99%BC%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%B3%E5%B1%AC%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA?fbclid=IwY2xjawFGUzNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZR3bvJqopV2_FtOlyPTW6QUr8xctmwGyWdZbpFlTKvzbLE5yw48nAqM8w_aem_4Y3o8JLACKPv-Cd2oBbshw">星島</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">女網紅在北角廉政公署總部大樓門外打卡，帖文更寫上「ICAC 查案！不方便透露！這裡是 TVB 迷來香港必去的吧！」。她一身西裝的打扮，又向網友展示印有她姓名的「廉政公署執行處授權證」，當中印有其「首席調查主任」的職級、證件號碼和證件有效期。她事後被網民指控偽造證件及冒充廉政公署人員，目前女子已經將小紅書上的所有帖文刪除。有關事件曝光後，有網民發現小紅書上原來充斥着大量類似的偽造證件情況，不少遊客到廉署打卡時都會出示自己偽造的 ICAC 證件，亦有人會為自己喜愛的藝人偽造證件，包括古天樂、陳奕迅和一眾韓星，更有人表示可以提供模版供他人製作相關的 ICAC 證件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261166 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0040red-423x580.jpg" alt="" width="423" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0040red-423x580.jpg 423w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0040red.jpg 656w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 423px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1261165 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0037red-478x580.jpg" alt="" width="478" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0037red-478x580.jpg 478w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img20240904wa0037red.jpg 738w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 478px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2021470/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BAICAC-%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E7%99%BC%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%B3%E5%B1%AC%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA?fbclid=IwY2xjawFGUzNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZR3bvJqopV2_FtOlyPTW6QUr8xctmwGyWdZbpFlTKvzbLE5yw48nAqM8w_aem_4Y3o8JLACKPv-Cd2oBbshw">星島</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">廉政公署就事件作出回應，引用《廉政公署條例》第 13C 條，指冒充廉署人員即屬犯罪 ，一經定罪最高可被判處監禁一年及罰款 25,000 元。網民對事件的反應各有不同，有人認為女子行為屬於違法亦有人認為女子只是 Cosplay 不屬違法，有人就表示不理解到廉政公署打卡的行為。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2021470/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BAICAC-%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E7%99%BC%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%86%92%E5%85%85%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8D%B3%E5%B1%AC%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA?fbclid=IwY2xjawFGUzNleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHZR3bvJqopV2_FtOlyPTW6QUr8xctmwGyWdZbpFlTKvzbLE5yw48nAqM8w_aem_4Y3o8JLACKPv-Cd2oBbshw">星島</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/little-red-book-girl-pictures-in-hkicac-crime-of-forgery/hottopic/spotlight/">小紅書充斥假證有網紅更到廉署打卡，或涉及偽造證件及冒充廉政公署人員</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
